\[\min_{x,y\in V_{p}}L(x,y)=\langle x^{*},y^{*}\rangle-1=\cos(\gamma)-1=2\cos^{ 2}\frac{\gamma}{2}-2=2\frac{(1-\theta+\langle\varphi(p),c\rangle)^{2}}{\| \varphi(p)+c\|^{2}}-2=\epsilon.\]

